Classes in alphabetsoup.waypointgraph used by alphabetsoup.simulators.combinatorialmarkettaskallocation
Waypoint
          Waypoint represents a location and any objects that are relevant to that location, such as Buckets, Bucket storage locations, WordStations, and LetterStations.
WaypointGraph
          WaypointGraph maintains a collection of connected Waypoints, and the associated ways to reference and manage them.
